# Leak-prevention safety net ONLY — private profile-extension/state files do NOT live
# here. They resolve from ~/.mo/operator (or MO_OPERATOR_PACK) under the user's
# MO profile; this checkout is the one public product repo and never a submodule
# host. The resolver never reads a repo-local copy; local maintainer tests cover
# that boundary from the ignored tests/ overlay. This line only guarantees a stray
# hand-copied operator/ can never be committed.
operator/
# Ignored local docs are not product authority; track product-safe guidance or
# keep private/local records under ~/.mo/memory.
docs/
